&lt;h2 id="you-have-to-stick-your-neck-out-and-be-willing-to-fail-publicly"&gt;You have to stick your neck out and be willing to fail publicly&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nivi:&lt;/strong&gt; We finished discussing the tweetstorm. We&amp;rsquo;re going to spend some time on Q&amp;amp;A and discussing tweets that didn&amp;rsquo;t make it into the &amp;ldquo;How to Get Rich&amp;rdquo; tweetstorm. My first question: What are some common failures or things people typically do wrong when they try to apply this advice?&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>There's No Actual Skill Called “Business”</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/theres-no-actual-skill-called-business/</link><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2019 15:13:52 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/theres-no-actual-skill-called-business/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/theres-no-actual-skill-called-business.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
