&lt;h1 id="use-the-wastebasket"&gt;Use the wastebasket&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is a mistake to suppose that men succeed through success; they much oftener succeed through failures. Precept, study, advice, and example could never have taught them so well as failure has done.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Samuel Smiles&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Not every idea leads to a success, and not every first draft forms a good template for the final draft.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>How Not to Die</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/die/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/die/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_zh/die/"&gt;Chinese Version&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
